        "translations": {
          "en": "Regarding His saying, the Mighty and Majestic: 'When he recovered, he said: Glory be to You! I repent to You, and I am the first of the believers.' He said: It means: Glory be to You, I repent to You for asking to see You, and I am the first of the believers that You cannot be seen.",
